Super Bowl at MetLife Stadium in New Jersey to Be Feb. 2, 2014, NFL Says

-- B y   M i c h a e l   S i l l u p
-- 
2011-10-11T16:33:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/super-bowl-at-metlife-stadium-in-new-jersey-to-be-feb-2-2014-nfl-says.html
The  Super Bowl  at MetLife Stadium in
 East Rutherford ,  New Jersey , will be held on Feb. 2, 2014,
National Football League spokesman  Greg Aiello  said on Twitter.  The stadium, which is home to the  New York Giants  and Jets,
was awarded the 2014 NFL title game last year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net  